tion of the immune system and contributes to normal formation of red blood cells and haemoglobin.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Pre 9+ Care Gold | Blackmores Club TH EN Member Sign Up Find Store Healthy Tips Products Favorite Pack World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Ask the Expert --> News & Activities Blackmores Video News & Activities Blackmores Video Ask the Expert --> World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Products Favorite Pack Healthy Tips Find Store  Log In Member Sign Up TH EN Health & Remedies      Health Hub       ALL Blackmores Pre 9+ Care Gold About this product 21 nutrients, multivitamin and mineral (include CoQ10 and DHA) Features • Folic acid contributes to normal red blood formation & amino acid synthesis • Iodine contributes to normal function of the nervous system. • Iron contributes to the normal function of the immune system and contributes to normal formation of red blood cells and haemoglobin. Dosage Dosage: Adult - Take 1 capsule with meal once a day Active ingredients Active ingredient per capsule: Fish Oil 250 mg Per capsule contains 250 mg of fish oil which provide Omega-3, including polyunsaturated fatty acids; EPA (Eicosapentaenoic acid) 25 mg DHA (Docosahexaenoic acid) 125 mg Saturated fat 190 mg   Magnesium 53 mg (from Magnesium citrate 67.9 mg and Magnesium oxide 69.7 mg) Coenzyme Q10 30 mg   Choline Bitartrate 25 mg Iron 7.7 mg (from Ferrous fumarate 23.55 mg)   Zinc 6 mg (from Zinc sulphate monohydrate 16.6 mg) Vitamin E 13.6 IU (from D-alpha-tocopheryl acetate 80% 12.5 mg)   Nicotinamide 10 mg Manganese 1.75 mg (from Manganese sulphate monohydrate 5.39 mg)   Pantothenic acid 2.3 mg (from Calcium pantothenate 2.51 mg) Betacarotene 750 mcg (from Betacarotene 30% 2.5 mg)   Vitamin B6 2 mg (from Pyridoxine hydrochloride 2.43 mg) Vitamin B12 2 mcg (from Cyanocobalamin 0.1% 2mg)   Vitamin B1 750 mcg (from Thiamin mononitrate 925 mcg) Vitamin B2 750 mcg (Riboflavin 750 mcg)   Folic acid 200 mcg Chromium 25 mcg (from Chromium chloride hexahydrate 131 mcg)   Vitamin D3 200 IU (from Vitamin D3 2,000,000 IU/G 100 mcg) Iodine 75 mcg (from Potassium iodide 97.86 mcg)   Selenium 32 .5 mcg (from Selenomethionine 81.3 mcg) Biotin 50 mcg   Available size 30 capsules Cautions Cautions Do not use if allergy to marine fish or fish oil Warning for people who have slow blood clotting or use anti-coagulation or aspirin Food Allergen Information: Contains Fish and soybean products Always read the label before use. To read a warning statement on a label before consuming. No effect for prevention or cure diseases. Children and pregnant women should not be consumed. Should eat varieties of five categories food in appropriate proportion. ฆอ. 1843/2564 | โฆษณานี้ได้รับการอนุญาตจากสำนักงานคณะกรรมการอาหารและยา Just a sore throat? 11 ways to Japanese longevity BE OUR MEMBER To get special privilege, news and promotions. To get special privilege, news and promotions. FIND A STORE Find a nearby store location --> Choose to receive our e-newsletter and get many more privileges from Blackmores -->  ฉันได้อ่านและยอมรับ  นโยบายความเป็นส่วนตัว  และ  นโยบายการให้ความยินยอม  เรียบร้อยแล้ว Get News BlackmoresTH Blackmores Thailand Healthy tips @Livemoreclub Healthy aging tips @50morefitandfun @2015 all rights reserved. Blackmores Thailand | Terms & Condition | Privacy Policies | Editorial Policy | Contact Us","productImportId":"35b3016f-53c5-4750-a9ac-a35fc6c7652f","aiFactCorrection":{"notes":"Mapped 21 ingredients to canonical catalogue using per-capsule active ingredient table; corrected Selenium amount to 32.5 mcg from source text; normalized B-vitamin and choline names to canonical forms.","responseId":"4471eb5c-7f2f-9e41-b70a-04b9a41b6118","correctedAt":"2026-05-18T17:12:39.959Z","originalFactCount":21,"correctedFactCount":21},"activeIngredientCount":21,"structuredIngredients":[],"candidateSupplierReason":"