 also supports joint health, promotes collagen formation, and helps maintain immune system health. This formulation supports general health and wellbeing, and helps maintain vitamin and mineral levels in the body. Ideal for those seeking daily support for mobility, comfort and inflammation relief in one convenient tablet. Good health changes everything. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Inflammation Mild Joint Pain Joint Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits A dual-action formula to relieve inflammation and pain. Containing curcumin for anti-inflammatory action and PEA as an analgesic. Relieves mild joint pain. Supports immune system health. Analgesic to relieve pain. Relieves pain after exercise. Supports general health and wellbeing. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Contains bioavailable TurmXTRA® 60N curcumin, formulated for optimal absorption. Bioavailable palmidrol PEA from Levagen+, formulated for optimal absorption. Dosage Adults For anti-inflammatory action : Take 2 tablets once a day. To relieve pain : Take 3 tablets once a day. Do not exceed 3 tablets in 24 hours. Do not use for more than 21 consecutive days. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Do not use if you have pre-existing liver conditions. In very rare cases, Curcuma species may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. The medicine may interact with other prescription analgesic medicines, please consult your healthcare practitioner before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings A dual-action formula to relieve inflammation and pain. Containing curcumin for anti-inflammatory action and PEA as an analgesic. Relieves mild joint pain. Supports immune system health. Analgesic to relieve pain. Relieves pain after exercise. Supports general health and wellbeing. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Contains bioavailable TurmXTRA® 60N curcumin, formulated for optimal absorption. Bioavailable palmidrol PEA from Levagen+, formulated for optimal absorption. Adults For anti-inflammatory action : Take 2 tablets once a day. To relieve pain : Take 3 tablets once a day. Do not exceed 3 tablets in 24 hours. Do not use for more than 21 consecutive days. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Do not use if you have pre-existing liver conditions. In very rare cases, Curcuma species may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. The medicine may interact with other prescription analgesic medicines, please consult your healthcare practitioner before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Palmidrol (PEA from Levagen+) 150.1 mg Curcuma longa (as TurmXTRA® 6