your immune defences (post exercise) and support immune system health through gut-immune activation.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Gut Immune Biotic All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Gut Immune Biotic Size Size 60 tablets Your gut is more than digestion, it’s the powerhouse of your immune system. Approximately 70% of your immune cells live in the gut*, working as your body’s first line of defence to protect and prevent illness. That’s why supporting the gut–immune connection is essential for everyday resilience. Blackmores Gut Immune Biotic is formulated with clinically trialled postbiotic Wellmune®, High-strength Vitamin C and zinc. Postbiotics are beneficial compounds produced by probiotics during fermentation, delivering targeted health benefits without requiring live bacteria. Backed by science and crafted with care, Gut Immune Biotic™ is designed for those who want to stay strong, active, and healthy every day. *Wiertsema SP et al. The Interplay between the Gut Microbiome and the Immune System in the Context of Infectious Diseases throughout Life and the Role of Nutrition in Optimizing Treatment Strategies. Nutrients. 2021 Mar 9;13(3):886. doi: 10.3390/nu13030886 Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Gut Flora Common Colds & Flu Digestive Health General Health Immune System Health No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports healthy gastrointestinal immune function. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Enhances immune defence (post exercise). Supports immune system to fight illness. Helps stimulate a healthy immune system response after exercise. Supports vitamin C and zinc levels in the body. Decreases common cold duration and the severity of common cold symptoms. Supports healthy mucous membranes and mucous tissue of the respiratory tract. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your healthcare professional before use. Adults only. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. 