is, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Sugar Balance™ Size Size 90 tablets BLACKMORES Sugar Balance is formulated with chromium, zinc and magnesium—nutrients that work together to help your body manage energy and sugar metabolism. It provides support to help maintain healthy blood sugar, aid sugar and carbohydrate metabolism, and support energy levels. The inclusion of antioxidants helps reduce free radicals formed in the body, while zinc and magnesium contribute to supporting heart health and nutrient metabolism. Taken daily, this balanced nutritional formula assists in maintaining wellbeing for those mindful of sugar levels and energy needs. Good health changes everything—support daily metabolism and energy balance with BLACKMORES Sugar Balance. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Provides chromium, an essential nutrient needed for sugar metabolism Contains nutrients to support blood sugar levels which may be lost due to changes in diet and exercise habits. Aids protein, fat and carbohydrate metabolism. Supports and regulates the production of energy from the metabolism of food. Chromium and manganese are utilised by the body to aid in efficient uptake of blood sugar into the body cells where it is burned as fuel. Maintains energy production and levels. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or if you have pre-existing diabetes, consult your health professional before use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. [Contains vitamin B6]. Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions, are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Provides chromium, an essential nutrient needed for sugar metabolism Contains nutrients to support blood sugar levels which may be lost due to changes in diet and exercise habits. Aids protein, fat and carbohydrate metabolism. Supports and regulates the production of energy from the metabolism of food. Chromium and manganese are utilised by the body to aid in efficient uptake of blood sugar into the body cells where it is burned as fuel. Maintains energy production and levels. Adults Take 1 tablet three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or if you have pre-existing diabetes, consult your health professional before use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. [Contains vitamin B6]. Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions, are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Chromic chloride hexahydrate 256 micrograms equivalent chromium 50 micrograms Chromium picolinate 134 micrograms equivalent chromium 16.6 micrograms Thiamine nitrate 7 mg equivalent thiamine (vitamin B1) 5.67 mg Riboflavin (vitamin B2) 8 mg Nicotinamide 35 mg Calcium pantothenate 7 mg equivalent pantothenic acid (vitamin B5) 6.41 mg Pyridoxine hydrochloride 8 mg equivalent pyridoxine (vitamin B6) 6.58 mg Cyanocobalamin (vitamin B12) 17 micrograms Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 30 mg Colecalciferol 3.35 micrograms equivalent vitamin D3 134 IU Folic acid 70 micrograms Heavy magnesium oxide 166 mg equivalent magnesium 100 mg Manganese amino acid chelate 7 mg equivalent manganese 700 micrograms Zinc amino acid chelate 20 mg equivalent zinc 4 mg Show More Sugar Balance™ Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our 