dText":"Blackmores Omega Triple Super Strength Fish Oil All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Omega Triple Super Strength Fish Oil Size Size 150 capsules Blackmores Omega Triple Super Strength Fish Oil delivers a high-concentration dose of omega-3s in each capsule, designed to support your wellbeing in multiple ways. Taken daily, it helps relieve symptoms of mild arthritis, including inflammation and mild joint swelling, and is ideal for people needing joint support. This formula also helps support cardiovascular system health and heart health, while assisting with nervous system, brain health and cognitive function. It contributes to general health and wellbeing, and helps support eye and skin health as part of your omega-3 intake. Extracted from 100% wild-caught fish and purified for quality, it’s a powerful choice for whole-body support - because good health changes everything. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Mild Arthritis Inflammation Heart and Cardiovascular Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Contains concentrated fish omega-3. Super strength, odourless capsule. Relieves inflammation and symptoms of mild arthritis. Helps maintain healthy blood fats and heart health. Three times more omega-3 per capsule than our Fish Oil 1000. Rigorously tested for mercury, dioxins and PCBs. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Take only ONE of the following dose recommendations, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Adults As an omega-3 supplement and for heart health: Take 1 capsule once a day. To help maintain healthy blood fats: Take 2 capsules once a day. For mild joint inflammation and symptoms of mild arthritis: Take 3 capsules once a day. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish, sulfites and soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains concentrated fish omega-3. Super strength, odourless capsule. Relieves inflammation and symptoms of mild arthritis. Helps maintain healthy blood fats and heart health. Three times more omega-3 per capsule than our Fish Oil 1000. Rigorously tested for mercury, dioxins and PCBs. Supports general health and wellbeing. Take only ONE of the following dose recommendations, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Adults As an omega-3 supplement and for heart health: Take 1 capsule once a day. To help maintain healthy blood fats: Take 2 capsules once a day. For mild joint inflammation and symptoms of mild arthritis: Take 3 capsules once a day. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish, sulfites and soya bean products. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Concentrated fish omega-3 triglycerides 1500 mg (1.5 g) containing omega-3 triglycerides 900 mg equivalent eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 540 mg equivalent docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 360 mg Omega Triple Super Strength Fish Oil Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia 