ralisation. This formula also supports calcium absorption in bones, contributes to muscle function, and helps maintain general health and wellbeing. Ideal for adults whose diets may be low in calcium, it offers daily support in a tablet form. Good health changes everything—support your bones and muscles every day with Blackmores. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Bone Health Muscle Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Contains 3 forms of calcium plus cofactors including magnesium, vitamin D3. Supports calcium absorption in bones. Supports vitamin D3 levels in the body. Helps maintain bone mineralisation and strength. Supports bone health. Supports muscle function. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet, 3 times a day with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding consult your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains phenylalanine, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains 3 forms of calcium plus cofactors including magnesium, vitamin D3. Supports calcium absorption in bones. Supports vitamin D3 levels in the body. Helps maintain bone mineralisation and strength. Supports bone health. Supports muscle function. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet, 3 times a day with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as pres