p - Day and Night Formula - All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Stress & Sleep Size Size 20 tablets BLACKMORES Stress & Sleep® is a dual-action formula combining B vitamins in the day tablet with valerian extract in the night tablet. Taken in the morning, it helps maintain energy levels, support cognitive function, and support a healthy stress response in the body. At night, the formula helps reduce the time to fall asleep and support refreshing sleep. Designed for those seeking support for both stress and sleep, this convenient day-to-night solution fits seamlessly into your routine. BLACKMORES Stress & Sleep® supports how you feel from day through to night—because good health changes everything. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Sleep Stress Energy No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Your sleeping patterns can affect how you feel throughout the day, so it is important to be well rested in order to help clear your mind. 1 Blackmores Stress & Sleep formula: Provides dual action for stress and sleep support. Is convenient for everyday use, morning and night. Day tablet is specifically formulated with B vitamins for energy levels. Night tablet contains a valerian extract that relieves nervous tension and is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to induce sleep. https://www.headtohealth.gov.au/meaningful-life/physical-health/sleep Dosage Adults Day Tablet (Mega B Complex) - Take 1 tablet once a day, with food. Night Tablet (Valerian Forte) - Take 1 tablet once a day, 30 minutes to 1 hour before bedtime. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing of the skin/eyes, dark urine, nausea, vomiting, unusual tiredness, weakness, abdominal pain, and/or loss of appetite, stop using this product and see your doctor. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible [Contains vitamin B6]. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Your sleeping patterns can affect how you feel throughout the day, so it is important to be well rested in order to help clear your mind. 1 Blackmores Stress & Sleep formula: Provides dual action for stress and sleep support. Is convenient for everyday use, morning and night. Day tablet is specifically formulated with B vitamins for energy levels. Night tablet contains a valerian extract that relieves nervous tension and is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to induce sleep. https://www.headtohealth.gov.au/meaningful-life/physical-health/sleep Adults Day Tablet (Mega B Complex) - Take 1 tablet once a day, with food. Night Tablet (Valerian Forte) - Take 1 tablet once a day, 30 minutes to 1 hour before bedtime. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing of the skin/eyes, dark urine, nausea, vomiting, unusual tiredness, weakness, abdominal pain, and/or loss of appetite, stop using this product and see your doctor. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible [Contains vitamin B6]. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per day tablet (Mega B Complex): Thiamine hydrochloride (vitamin B1) 50 mg Riboflavin (vitamin B2) 30 mg Nicotinamide 100 mg Calcium pantothenate 50 mg equivalent pantothenic acid (vitamin B5) 45.81 mg Pyridoxine h