h":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Joint Formula Advanced Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Joint Formula Advanced Size Size 60 tablets 120 tablets Good health changes everything—support joint health with Blackmores Joint Formula Advanced. This formulation combines glucosamine sulfate, chondroitin, manganese and boron to help relieve symptoms of mild arthritis, including mild joint pain, swelling, and stiffness. It supports healthy joint cartilage production, mobility, and flexibility, while also helping to maintain bone health and support general wellbeing. With ingredients that assist healthy bone development and bone mineralisation, it’s designed to provide daily support for joint comfort and movement. Taken twice daily with meals, it offers a convenient way to manage mild joint concerns. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Osteoarthritis Mild Joint Pain Joint Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Reduces symptoms of mild osteoarthritis: -Reduces mild joint inflammation and swelling. -Reduces mild joint aches and pains. -Reduces mild joint stiffness. -Maintains joint mobility and flexibility. -Maintains healthy joint cartilage production. Sustainably sourced form of non-GMO glucosamine sulfate (Glucosagreen®). Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet, twice a day with a meal or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake in inadequate. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your healthcare professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites and soya bean products. Contains approx. 223 mg sodium per daily dose. Benefits Dosage Warnings Reduces symptoms of mild osteoarthritis: -Reduces mild joint inflammation and swelling. -Reduces mild joint aches and pains. -Reduces mild joint stiffness. -Maintains joint mobility and flexibility. -Maintains healthy joint cartilage production. Sustainably sourced form of non-GMO glucosamine sulfate (Glucosagreen®). Adults Take 1 tablet, twice a day with a meal or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake in inadequate. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your healthcare professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites and soya bean products. Contains approx. 223 mg sodium per daily dose. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Bovine sodium chondroitin sulfate 400 mg Glucosamine sulfate sodium chloride 942 mg equivalent glucosamine sulfate 750 mg Manganese gluconate 8.77 mg equiv manganese 1 mg Borax 8.83 mg equiv boron 1 mg Joint Formula Advanced Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Term