  ('230a3f7a-a2fb-4c43-8561-6e521dec0533'::uuid, 'f829101b-28c7-40af-a5cc-334321374a09'::uuid, null, 'product_updated', 'codex_blackmores_clean_approval', '{"id":"f829101b-28c7-40af-a5cc-334321374a09","title":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus","region":"TH","source":"manufacturer_import","status":"pending_review","brand_id":"40e4806a-5049-4668-8d29-ab36a31202dd","category":null,"currency":"THB","platform":"manual","title_en":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus","title_th":null,"image_url":"https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt948bd74310fc0ad0/blt1ddd832e785431a3/68c752937253059b4e8cdea2/93575805-1.webp","brand_name":"blackmores","created_at":"2026-05-21T13:09:46.322+00:00","source_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/joint-mobility-plus","updated_at":"2026-05-21T13:09:46.343167+00:00","admin_notes":null,"description":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus contains collagen to support joint mobility and relieve mild joint pains in active individuals.","product_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/joint-mobility-plus","label_status":"parsed","price_amount":null,"product_kind":"supplement","description_en":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus contains collagen to support joint mobility and relieve mild joint pains in active individuals.","description_th":null,"normalized_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/joint-mobility-plus","current_version":1,"fda_verified_at":null,"price_cached_at":null,"source_snapshot":{"dosage":"for use. Read the","locale":"en","parser":"blackmores_structured_ingredients_v2","titleEn":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus","htmlLength":163640,"validation":{"status":"pass","reasons":[],"summary":"3 matchable canonical facts.","checkedAt":"2026-05-21T13:09:46.333Z","matchableFactCount":3},"description":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus contains collagen to support joint mobility and relieve mild joint pains in active individuals.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus contains collagen to support joint mobility and relieve mild joint pains in active individuals.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus with UC-II® Collagen Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus Size Size 60 tablets Good health changes everything—support your active lifestyle with Blackmores Joint Mobility Plus. This advanced one-a-day formula combines UC-II® type II collagen, vitamin C and vitamin D to help relieve symptoms of mild osteoarthritis, including mild joint pain, stiffness, and aches. It also helps support healthy joint cartilage development, bone health, and muscle function, while assisting collagen formation and acting as an antioxidant to reduce free radicals in the body. Tailored for active individuals, it supports joint mobility, flexibility, and general wellbeing, offering daily joint care in a convenient chewable format. Product Format Chewable Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Osteoarthritis Joint Health Bone Health No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits One small orange flavoured chewable tablet a day. Helps improve joint mobility in mild osteoarthritis from as early as 30 days* Maintains joint health, mild stiffness and flexibility in active individuals. With UC-II® to reduce mild joint aches and pains in active individuals. Reduces joint discomfort associated with mild osteoarthritis Support collagen formation. Vitamin D helps absorption of dietary calcium which supports bone health. Vitamin C to help support healthy joint cartilage growth. Vitamin C to help support collagen health. *Tjandra O, et al. Efficacy and safety of Undenatured type II collagen in the treatment of osteoarthritis of the knee: a randomized, double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial. Indones Biomed J. 2023;15(3):277&ndash;86. This study was supported and funded by PT Pharos, Jakarta, Indonesia *Crowley DC, et al. Safety and efficacy of undenatured type II collagen in the treatment of osteoarthritis of the knee: a clinical trial. Int J Med Sci. 2009;6(6):312&ndash;21. This research was supported by InterHealth Research Center, CA Dosage Adults Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not use if you have allergies to sulfites or collagen. Supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains gluten, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings One small orange flavoured chewable tablet a day. Helps improve joint mobility in mild osteoarthritis from as early as 30 days* Maintains joint health, mild stiffness and flexibility in active individuals. With UC-II® to reduce mild joint aches and pains in active individuals. Reduces joint discomfort associated with mild osteoarthritis Support collagen formation. Vitamin D helps absorption of dietary calcium which supports bone health. Vitamin C to help support healthy joint cartilage growth. Vitamin C to help support collagen health. *Tjandra O, et al. Efficacy and safety of Undenatured type II collagen in the treatment of osteoarthritis of the knee: a randomized, double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial. Indones Biomed J. 2023;15(3):277&ndash;86. This study was supported and funded by PT Pharos, Jakarta, Indonesia *Crowley DC, et al. Safety and efficacy of undenatured type II collagen in the treatment of osteoarthritis of the knee: a clinical trial. Int J Med Sci. 2009;6(6):312&ndash;21. This research was supported by InterHealth Research Center, CA Adults Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not use if you have allergies to sulfites or collagen. Supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains gluten, soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per chewable tablet: Chicken sternum cartilage powder UC-II® 40 mg equivalent collagen 10 mg Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 50 mg Colecalciferol 10 micrograms equivalent vitamin D3 400 IU Joint Mobility Plus Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopath Product & Purchasing FAQs Blackmores Subscribe Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspected Adverse Experience Contact Us Ask a Naturopath Product & Purchasing FAQs Blackmores Subscribe Back To Top Terms of Purchase Privacy Policy ©2025 Blackmores. All Rights Reserved. ©2025 Blackmores. All Rights Reserved.","productImportId":"8c89a6a9-6a34-41cc-8116-ba40b7058bfa","aiFactCorrection":{"notes":"Mapped to canonical e