hop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Flaxseed Oil Size Size 100 capsules Blackmores Flaxseed Oil is an organic, plant-based source of essential fatty acids including omega-3, 6 and 9. Suitable for vegetarians, this formula is used to support general health and wellbeing, maintain cardiovascular system health, and support skin health when dietary intake is inadequate. Derived from cold-pressed flaxseeds, it’s an ideal alternative for individuals seeking non-fish omega sources. This naturally sourced oil helps bridge dietary gaps where essential fatty acids may be lacking. Blackmores Flaxseed Oil is free from artificial additives and preservatives. Good health changes everything—choose plant-based support with Blackmores Flaxseed Oil. Product Format Vegetarian Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Skin Health Heart and Cardiovascular Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports skin health if dietary intake is inadequate. Supports heart health. Vegetarian and organic source of omega-3,6,9. Supports general health and wellbeing. Rich source of omega 6 linolenic acid (LA). Dosage Adults For general health and wellbeing : Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. For skin health : Take 3 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. For cardiovascular/heart health: Take 2 capsules twice a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use if you are pregnant or breastfeeding. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports skin health if dietary intake is inadequate. Supports heart health. Vegetarian and organic source of omega-3,6,9. Supports general health and wellbeing. Rich source of omega 6 linolenic acid (LA). Adults For general health and wellbeing : Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. For skin health : Take 3 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. For cardiovascular/heart health: Take 2 capsules twice a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use 